g\" class=\"\" src=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/6u3a4nbQkfUicr5N72G2nEu58OrhB1NbPdudxtaavXOz8TAYs8Y8nDia9Fuyh385Jq5dj7KG0nkZs1k5t2Aqc66g/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&tp=webp&wxfrom=5&wx_lazy=1&wx_co=1\" alt=\"图片\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><img title=\"微信图片_20190719164833.jpg\" class=\"\" src=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/6u3a4nbQkfUicr5N72G2nEu58OrhB1NbPkUFVjFE3HLH0mV6U8MRUSwwN2ibSYvuop8jghPqiauiaWrzjjqOSPVvuw/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&tp=webp&wxfrom=5&wx_lazy=1&wx_co=1\" alt=\"图片\"/></p></section></section></section></section></section></section><section><section><section><section><section><section><section><section><section><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: PingFangTC-ultralight;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-style: italic;\">&nbsp;Day2<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">&nbsp;</span></span></span></strong></p></section></section></section></section></section></section><section><section><section><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-align: left; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">•&nbsp;酒店自助早餐后，前往世界最高塔——<strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(24, 84, 210);\">【Burj Khalifa哈利法塔】</span></strong>观光，是迪拜的地标之一，高828米，共162层，电影《碟中谍4》中，阿汤哥大显身手徒手攀爬哈利法塔。在124层观景台上，通过360度玻璃幕墙鸟瞰整个迪拜全景，可将棕榈岛、帆船酒店等尽收眼底，颇为壮观。<br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-align: left; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">•&nbsp;下午将全方位观赏有“世界上最大的人工岛”、“世界第八大景”之称的<strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(24, 84, 210);\">【The Palm棕榈岛】</span></strong>，棕榈岛呈棕榈树的形状，岛上遍布度假酒店和豪宅。岛上最著名的建筑就是位于尽头的亚特兰蒂斯度假酒店，到月牙形的堤坝上，可以看到一望无际的大海，回头便可看到亚特兰蒂斯酒店的全景，这里也是拿酒店做背景拍照的最佳地点。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-align: left; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">•&nbsp;随即近距离观赏六星级<strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(24, 84, 210);\">【Atlantis The Palm&nbsp;亚特兰蒂斯酒店】</span></strong>，此酒店耗资15亿美元兴建，位于棕榈岛的尽头，占地113亩，体现了古波斯和古巴比伦建筑装潢风貌。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-align: left; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">• 棕榈岛看点颇多，爱摄影的您，尽是发挥之处 ！留影后于亚特兰蒂斯酒店享用高档国际自助餐。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-align: left; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">•&nbsp;<strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(24, 84, 210);\">【迪拜冲沙】</span></strong><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; caret-color: rgb(102, 102, 102); color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">在迪拜专属沙漠区域进行冲沙</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; caret-color: rgb(102, 102, 102); color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">，该区沙子柔细，连绵起伏，层次感强，在落日的映照下呈红金色，非常具有观赏性。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 20px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-align: start; line-height: 26px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">沙漠向导将用豪华四驱越野车带您体验精彩刺激的震颤之旅，从高高的沙丘顶上欣赏夕阳西下，继而日暮时分前往独具风格特色的传统阿拉伯风格营地，可以选择小酌小饮（阿拉伯咖啡、茶、软饮、酒类均免费），或者体验骑骆驼，或者也可以让阿拉伯画师为您在手臂上画上精美的汉娜花，或者您还可以体验各种口味的阿拉伯水烟。璀璨星光下的盛宴上备有烤肉，新鲜沙拉，以及多种阿拉伯甜点，随着鼓点声起，美丽的舞娘带来了迷人的肚皮舞表演，您也可以上台与其共舞。熄灯片刻，您可以凝望星空，体验久违的远离城市喧嚣的宁静和惬意。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-align: left; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><img class=\"__bg_gif\" title=\"微信图片_20190719164935.gif\" src=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_gif/6u3a4nbQkfUicr5N72G2nEu58OrhB1NbPTYKQbJWq4osMOwPibYQ1Lyiba8UMUcsRRCc4qdXf5GPS8OEJsNb1ytAQ/640?wx_fmt=gif&tp=webp&wxfrom=5&wx_lazy=1\" alt=\"图片\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><img title=\"微信图片_20190719164849.jpg\" class=\"\" src=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/6u3a4nbQkfUicr5N72G2nEu58OrhB1NbP92OjdOvxfA4CWFzDqDSJ2zamRzekwvAqlF67aaNT0wblcCCqoNUia7A/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&tp=webp&wxfrom=5&wx_lazy=1&wx_co=1\" alt=\"图片\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><img title=\"微信图片_20190719164857.jpg\" class=\"\" src=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/6u3a4nbQkfUicr5N72G2nEu58OrhB1NbPqOyYGVCibNjPhtXNYELX672P1rLra4vVr5D0Yq40ThzqMOA4tdBl4ow/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&tp=webp&wxfrom=5&wx_lazy=1&wx_co=1\" alt=\"图片\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><img title=\"微信图片_20190719164902.jpg\" class=\"\" src=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/6u3a4nbQkfUicr5N72G2nEu58OrhB1NbPtGqMBBK9icqqhMwRjiaRfA8pic08Jqm0nPgW8E9rSdytf5mEHvkOG9llQ/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&tp=webp&wxfrom=5&wx_lazy=1&wx_co=1\" alt=\"图片\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><img title=\"微信图片_20190719164907.jpg\" class=\"\" src=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/6u3a4nbQkfUicr5N72G2nEu58OrhB1NbPyrUfF2YzHM7XS8wzgvLs26yqvk14J5eAYxEfan8DTmR6GvQxwPX5FA/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&tp=webp&wxfrom=5&wx_lazy=1&wx_co=1\" alt=\"图片\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><img title=\"微信图片_20190719164911.jpg\" class=\"\" src=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/6u3a4nbQkfUicr5N72G2nEu58OrhB1NbPRSrkUeApyicV6rpw6sxhUS9ibPWo5q16v3SMLqd3paar7NBy1Y4ic8RCg/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&tp=webp&wxfrom=5&wx_lazy=1&wx_co=1\" alt=\"图片\"/></p></section></section></section></section></section></section><section><section><section><section><section><section><section><section><section><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: PingFangTC-ultralight;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-style: italic;\">&nbsp;Day3<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">&nbsp;</span></span></span></strong></p></section></section></section></section></section></section><section><section><section><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-align: left; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">•&nbsp;酒店早餐后前往<strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(24, 84, 210);\">【迪拜相框】</span></strong>，“迪拜之框”始建于2013年，高度约150米，宽93米。最令人称奇的是其外表全部贴金，建筑物内部共分50层，设有一条霓虹灯通道通往未来展览馆，游客可观赏有关未来五十年阿联酋发展的展览。大家可以从“相框”顶部眺望德伊勒古城至谢赫扎耶德路一带的壮阔景观。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-align: left; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">•&nbsp;中餐后去到<strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(24, 84, 210);\">【迪拜联合博物馆】</span></strong>，通过高科技把阿联酋建国史展现给世人，充分了解迪拜的地理、政治、经济及文化等多方面信息。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-align: left; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-align: left; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">•结束后去参观追梦公司在管理项目及办公地点。然后去</span><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(24, 84, 210);\">项目实地考察</span></strong><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">，感受项目真实的地理优势及景观。结束后从项目附近码头</span><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(24, 84, 210);\">乘坐豪华游艇出海</span></strong>，随着游艇穿梭高楼林立的Dubai Marina海滨新城，近距离、变角度观赏知名的建筑楼宇。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; text-align: left;\">•&nbsp;晚上在世界最高最大的</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; text-align: left; color: rgb(24, 84, 210);\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">【Dubai Fountain音乐喷泉】</strong></span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; text-align: left;\">边享用美食。</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; text-align: left;\">迪拜喷泉位于哈利法塔底部。</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; text-align: left;\">它拥有全球规模最大的编舞喷泉系统，喷水量多达22000 加仑，每一次拔地而起的水柱都高达 150 米。</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; text-align: left;\">喷薄而出的水柱缤纷多彩，随着音