 1em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br/></p></section></section></section><section><section><section><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><img title=\"微信图片_20190719170812.jpg\" class=\"\" src=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/6u3a4nbQkfUicr5N72G2nEu58OrhB1NbPbgaPjNBaZDQib1ocpweMphgavbCnHjaDJ9NHUPxwCKyia9FqPfTEnyaA/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&tp=webp&wxfrom=5&wx_lazy=1&wx_co=1\" alt=\"图片\"/></p></section></section></section><section><section><section><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-align: left; color: rgb(120, 117, 117); overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; text-decoration-line: underline; color: rgb(24, 84, 210); overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-style: italic;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 18px;\">*【刷卡】</span></strong></span></span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(73, 72, 72);\">除了带部分美金现金外，最好带上信用卡或银联卡。VISA和万事达卡绝对通用。商场大部分品牌现在也开始接受62开头的银联卡，汇率更优且无手续费，而且支持ATM取现。支付宝目前有些景点及部分品牌店也可用。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(120, 117, 117); overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-align: left; color: rgb(120, 117, 117); overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(73, 72, 72);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-style: italic; color: rgb(24, 84, 210);\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 18px;\">*【穿衣指南】</span></strong></span></span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(73, 72, 72);\">迪拜太阳照射比较强烈，最好穿着透气性好的衣服，在身体暴露部位要涂抹防晒霜。<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Arial, SimSun, STHeiti;\">如果需要长时间在室外活动，可以再加一件防晒服，以防皮肤被晒伤，并且需要戴墨镜、遮阳帽。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(120, 117, 117); overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-align: left; color: rgb(120, 117, 117); overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-size: 16px; font-family: Arial, SimSun, STHeiti;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-style: italic; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(24, 84, 210);\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 18px;\">*【小费】</span></strong></span></span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(73, 72, 72);\">在阿联酋也有给小费的习惯，可以酌情给予服务生、司机、导游等小费，一般一天给1美元即可。入住酒店的话第二天早上可以在床头柜上放置1美元纸钞。有些高级餐厅可能需要付总餐费的10%-17%。结账时请看清账单，有些已经包含服务费的就不需要再额外给了。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(120, 117, 117); overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-align: left; color: rgb(120, 117, 117); overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; text-decoration-line: underline; color: rgb(24, 84, 210); overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-style: italic;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 18px;\">*【用电插头】</span></strong></span></span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(73, 72, 72);\">迪拜的电压和国内是一样的，插头转换器基本酒店都能提供，超市机场也都能买到，如果一定要在国内购买，请买英标插座。</span></p></section></section></section></section><p></p><p><br/></p>', '1', '1', '1910', '0', '0', '2020-03-13', '2021-10-31', '2021-04-19 11:06:38', '2021-04-19 11:08:10');
