INSERT INTO `information` VALUES ('157', '1', '185', '74', 'uploads/images/mP0HQYKV1o.jpg', '想不到！三分之一的美国总统竟都是爱尔兰后裔', '爱尔兰血统承包美国总统！', '<p>说到爱尔兰对世界的输出和影响，你可能会想到每年三月十七日举目皆绿的圣帕特里克节（St. Patrick&#39;s Day）的庆祝活动；</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px;\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"text-align:center\"><img class=\"\" src=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/5a91TrSC18iat1KqibTn095I4IDdFrGiaiakFm1ByLL2oGkX32Q0SaKRicybjnutic0htkET35riaEzcqmAaE520iaEByg/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&tp=webp&wxfrom=5&wx_lazy=1&wx_co=1\" alt=\"图片\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \"><br/></p><p>或是举世闻名的爱尔兰作家叶芝的那首风靡全球的《当你老了》；</p><p><br/></p><p style=\"text-align:center\"><img src=\"http://ceshi.iaumeca.com:88/uploads/ueditor/image/20210416/1618545439718415.jpg\" title=\"1618545439718415.jpg\" alt=\"640.webp.jpg\"/></p><p><br/></p><p>或是令人热血沸腾的大河之舞</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.75em;\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"text-align:center\"><img class=\"\" src=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/5a91TrSC18iat1KqibTn095I4IDdFrGiaiaksGLYc8kEAyEzs3aBibZ2AhK6bmG3qZ7R9z6JfhQsljUUIe5Zk08ViaSg/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&tp=webp&wxfrom=5&wx_lazy=1&wx_co=1\" alt=\"图片\" width=\"645\" height=\"245\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px;\">但你们可能不知道的是，爱尔兰的血统基本包揽了美国总统的血统：</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \"><br/></p><section><section><section><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 16px;\">美国的45位总统中，</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 16px;\">居然有14位都是爱尔兰裔！</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 16px;\"><br/></span></p></strong></section></section></section><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px;\">下面小编给大家简单地盘点一下：</span></p><p><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(0, 82, 255); font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">1、安德鲁·杰克逊（AndrewJackson，第7任总统），他的父母出生在爱尔兰，1765年来到美国。</span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \"><br/></p><p style=\"text-align:center\"><img src=\"http://ceshi.iaumeca.com:88/uploads/ueditor/image/20210416/1618545490512766.jpg\" title=\"1618545490512766.jpg\" alt=\"640.webp (1).jpg\"/></p><p><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(0, 82, 255); font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">2、詹姆斯·波尔克（James Knox Polk，第11任总统），其曾曾祖父出生在爱尔兰，1680年移民美国。</span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(0, 82, 255); font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br/></span></strong></p><p style=\"text-align:center\"><img class=\"\" src=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/5a91TrSC18iat1KqibTn095I4IDdFrGiaiakG0URlxtThdP1x5R0kRdbxXxCTm7iaxQAdBzm2bQITJtmibTIeY02ACsg/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&tp=webp&wxfrom=5&wx_lazy=1&wx_co=1\" alt=\"图片\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \"><br/></p><p><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(0, 82, 255); font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.75em;\">3、詹姆斯·布坎南（James Buchanan，第15任总统），其父亲出生在爱尔兰，1783年来到费城。</span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(0, 82, 255); font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.75em;\"><br/></span></strong></p><p style=\"text-align:center\"><img class=\"\" src=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/5a91TrSC18iat1KqibTn095I4IDdFrGiaiakbpYknibGZejwORjic6RXUpBjc0P6l5G2jGvQztHRm6C8Yib9vfl5HwTOA/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&tp=webp&wxfrom=5&wx_lazy=1&wx_co=1\" alt=\"图片\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \"><br/></p><p><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px;\">&nbsp;</span><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(0, 82, 255); font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.75em;\">4、尤利塞斯·格兰特（Ulysses S Grant, 第18任总统），其母出生在爱尔兰。</span></strong><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; line-height: 1.75em; font-size: 15px;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; line-height: 1.75em; font-size: 15px;\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"text-align:center\"><img class=\"\" src=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/5a91TrSC18iat1KqibTn095I4IDdFrGiaiakrvE9p2wu1SxjGtgEkBlZkfWEYWxN3IugvWDw9RXWf1RV1ia1NrjRNvw/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&tp=webp&wxfrom=5&wx_lazy=1&wx_co=1\" alt=\"图片\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \"><br/></p><p><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(0, 82, 255); font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.75em;\">5、威廉·麦金莱（William McKinley, 第25任总统），其曾曾曾祖父来自爱尔兰。</span></strong><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; line-height: 1.75em; font-size: 15px;\">&nbsp;</span><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \"><br/></p><p style=\"text-align:center\"><img class=\"\" src=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/5a91TrSC18iat1KqibTn095I4IDdFrGiaiakSXianSaZ5tKwbmJXfE7Fx3F3iaKhqCZtO6AQPs5oX0G593dKB4XjQy0g/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&tp=webp&wxfrom=5&wx_lazy=1&wx_co=1\" alt=\"图片\"/></p><p><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; line-height: 1.75em; text-indent: 0em;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(0, 82, 255); font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.75em;\">6、西奥多·罗斯福（TheodoreRoosevelt, 第26任总统），曾祖父母1820年离开爱尔兰来到美国。</span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; line-height: 1.75em; text-indent: 0em;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(0, 82, 255); font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.75em;\"><br/></span></strong></p><p style=\"text-align:center\"><img class=\"\" src=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/5a91TrSC18iat1KqibTn095I4IDdFrGiaiakEEsgqDMk36wtsP6eUejVjVFSqvQfA3QwDSmh4UtGJWOYkTZdX7PUcA/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&tp=webp&wxfrom=5&wx_lazy=1&wx_co=1\" alt=\"图片\"/></p><p><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; line-height: 1.75em; text-indent: 0em;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(0, 82, 255); font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.75em;\">7、伍德罗·威尔逊（WoodrowWilson, 第28任总统），他的爱尔兰祖父1807年到达美国。</span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, 