 break-word !important; font-size: 15px;\">缴纳定金</span></p></li><li><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px;\">回国按照合同支付首期款和尾期款以及房产交易税、印花税（缴费进程由投资人把控）。</span></p></li></ul><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px;\">简单来讲，如果投资人全款购房，且资金快速到位，那么<strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">购房</strong><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">最快可以在两周内便可以完成。</strong></span></p></section></section></section><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><img class=\"rich_pages\" src=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/5a91TrSC18gcUuXqTGPvVVmM1Qpl1F7Zxm4h7aU53ibH01AlZAC9nNrLeIJzcVW84fJtPRqvT9gTNGehYiaySAnA/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&tp=webp&wxfrom=5&wx_lazy=1&wx_co=1\" alt=\"图片\"/></p><section><br/></section><section><section><section><section><section><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">下面以澳美家投资人P先生的实际经历为例，了解一下具体的获批流程</strong></p></section></section><section><section><section><section><section></section></section></section></section></section></section></section></section><section><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-align: center; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; letter-spacing: 1.5px; font-size: 15px;\"><br/></span></strong></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(252, 180, 65); letter-spacing: 1.5px;\">&nbsp;需求&nbsp;<br/></span></p></section><section><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px;\">投资人P先生考虑到女儿在葡萄牙念书，为了方便陪读，一心想要尽快拿到葡萄牙黄金居留卡，尽快完成全款和SEF递交事宜。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(252, 180, 65); font-size: 15px;\">&nbsp;购房&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px;\">在澳美家顾问的陪同下，P先生成功开好账户。P<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">先生</span>为了加快进展，亲自前往银行授权银行经理尽快完成全款转款事宜。在考察房产期间P<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">先生</span>就一直在和律师强调尽快预约地契过户的时间，表示会全力配合，律师也很快为投资人预约到地契过户的时间，三周后P<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">先生</span>顺利过户，拿到地契。P<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">先生</span>是3月20日签署的购房文件，4月12日成功拿到地契。</span></p></section><section><section><img class=\"\" src=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/5a91TrSC18gcUuXqTGPvVVmM1Qpl1F7ZtjmIaM6tYuhCxvO2Z58P960TV9yo94LCgmMaVfWkWSVGpXdVhBq4mQ/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&tp=webp&wxfrom=5&wx_lazy=1&wx_co=1\" alt=\"图片\"/></section></section><section><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(252, 180, 65); font-size: 15px;\">&nbsp;SEF递交&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px;\">P<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">先生</span>雷厉风行，在律师约好地契过户时间的前一周提前回到中国准备一家人的黄金居留许可项目文件，投资人隶属于上海领区，双认证文件于4月24日全部完成，P<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">先生</span>在当天将扫描件给到律师进行线上注册，线上注册后的缴费过程P<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">先生</span>也十分迅速，于5月15日完成一家人的线上注册和缴费事宜，正式进入线上审理阶段。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px;\">于5月20日收到SEF的线上通过通知(notification of acceptance)，意味着律师可以按照投资人的意愿和档期来预约录指纹时间了，P<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">先生</span>要求预约暑假的时间，这样不耽误女儿的学业。并且，P<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">先生在澳美家</span>了解到阿尔加维SEF审理只需要3-5个月，于是毫不犹豫的选择了阿尔加维SEF递交，可以看出澳美家的专业，P<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">先生</span>的申请进程是十分高效的。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br/></p></section><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><img class=\"rich_pages\" src=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/5a91TrSC18gcUuXqTGPvVVmM1Qpl1F7ZB2lQAmTfzia0UMXnUTyBLKJaLPZWEiaDYKcRFSFBA0uovZgnFYHnpT1g/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&tp=webp&wxfrom=5&wx_lazy=1&wx_co=1\" alt=\"图片\"/></p><section><br/></section><section><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">投资人P<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">先生</span>紧急需求之下选择了阿尔加维SEF，下面小编再以两位投资人为例，</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; text-decoration-line: underline; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">看一下<strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">阿尔加维、波尔图等SEF</strong>到底有多给力。</span></span></p></section><section><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br/></p></section><ul class=\" list-paddingleft-2\" style=\"padding: 0px 0px 0px 2.2em; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><li><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 1.5px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">澳美家投资人N女士18年9月24日在</span><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 1.5px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">阿尔加维SEF</span></strong><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 1.5px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">递交申请，于18年12月7日获批，</span><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1.5px;\">仅仅用时3个月</strong><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 1.5px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">，N女士缴纳制卡费之后于19年2月20日拿到黄金居留卡。</span><br/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; mi