ong></em><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(240, 131, 0);\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">柬埔寨人口红利巨大，人口结构年轻。</strong></span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px;\">整个柬埔寨平均年龄才27岁左右，8、9成的人口分布在0-50岁的区间，70%以上的人口不到34岁，而中国的平均年龄38岁，柬埔寨人整体比中国人年轻了10多岁，这正反映出柬埔寨将来的无限的可能性，从购买力、消费力、生产力等等方面来看，柬埔寨都体现出了强劲的动力。越年轻的国家，爆发的可能性越大，而反观日本由于人口老龄化过于严重，经济增长就呈现疲态。未来10年，将是柬埔寨的黄金10年。另外，27岁左右的人，正是处于成家立业的年龄段，未来几年对于房屋的刚性需求就非常大；</span></p></section><p><br/></p><section><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><em style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 24px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(240, 131, 0);\"><em style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><em style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 微软雅黑; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">9.&nbsp;</strong></em></strong></em></span></st